{"tid":1436259,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日肥窮獨男擁超靚女友　狂晒恩愛","createTime":"2019-08-09T09:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T16:47:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"97c3617194190511660e4dcdf8c2a6a6ce2940e3","tid":1436259,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:04:51.000Z","msg":"所謂的「勵志哥」，是泛指一些其貌不揚，但卻擁有女神般女友的男人，是能令所有男生都重燃人生希望的存在。<br />\n<br />\n近期日本出現一名Boss級的勵志哥，在肥窮醜毒的情況下，仍有一位超靚的女友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3134497/org/271b6bfe1ca04707232eded54df9170d.jpg/nsFUl7LioTGxlIkZEotb-WplnoZ_S4Zsa8spTmvLKU4?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3134497%2Forg%2F271b6bfe1ca04707232eded54df9170d.jpg%2FnsFUl7LioTGxlIkZEotb-WplnoZ_S4Zsa8spTmvLKU4%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=784eaec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（Twitter@DT43922294）<br />\n<br />\n這位勵志哥叫作ぱるぱる（Paru Paru），今年24歲，是一名人氣平平的Twitcasting直播主。除了肥窮醜毒之外，他還沒有任何正職或兼職工作。<br />\n<br />\n不過，他有一位交往了7個月的超靚女友，而且還經常於Twitter晒恩愛，令一眾網民超級羨慕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3134517/org/ea3fcd395d7cd6c7fd33aee1a9349533.jpg/GJySo_D1_T5E_rBp4v9EADLLgozTW7qiPGL9Bzxi_Qc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3134517%2Forg%2Fea3fcd395d7cd6c7fd33aee1a9349533.jpg%2FGJySo_D1_T5E_rBp4v9EADLLgozTW7qiPGL9Bzxi_Qc&h=482732b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3134530/org/6c02210bee612a0e5717c63e89385fb9.jpg/kwiOgYzz1AipfZgX7a6LMo0y9egNf6oT_zX_Qf81_0E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3134530%2Forg%2F6c02210bee612a0e5717c63e89385fb9.jpg%2FkwiOgYzz1AipfZgX7a6LMo0y9egNf6oT_zX_Qf81_0E&h=6a775ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無上進心兼軟飯王？<br />\n<br />\n通常看到這些極端例子時，正常人都會心想：「可能他是富二代或有上進心吧...」<br />\n<br />\n但事實卻並不是如此，在他開始交往後，就於Twitter上不停強調自己沒工作、超窮、廢青等等，還多次要女朋友請客接濟、買衣服給他，因此亦多了不少Haters。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3134525/org/b2a756a9461910646ab76834e89ec3ca.jpg/YJ3UOIFN1JtSpS1My6R7ulQLuga3oqI3fVcQTX1XEE0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3134525%2Forg%2Fb2a756a9461910646ab76834e89ec3ca.jpg%2FYJ3UOIFN1JtSpS1My6R7ulQLuga3oqI3fVcQTX1XEE0&h=9ef43ab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3134516/org/219be81fdbef7e722f5ca9121f6fc67f.jpg/m3kiHxWRW34vzEZ_ZbFp5jol9WYxOEULTyKg-k8ioPo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3134516%2Forg%2F219be81fdbef7e722f5ca9121f6fc67f.jpg%2Fm3kiHxWRW34vzEZ_ZbFp5jol9WYxOEULTyKg-k8ioPo&h=82695cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突然分手？<br />\n<br />\n近日，Paru Paru突然於Twitter公布他與女友分手的消息，原因是女友出軌。<br />\n<br />\n有網民還特意重溫他晒恩愛的舊文，製作4格漫畫以表達現實的殘酷；亦有不少網民熱烈狂賀。<br />\n<br />\n不過，女友其後在自己Twitter澄清Paru Paru的無理指控，表示自己並沒有出軌，只是他胡亂翻舊帳。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3134522/org/ebd5ce9f178be800ea86b00a82fc04bd.jpg/6LZi2Dz10aXZwWVovOT0ULZcn1osQTLGv3YNK792DSs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3134522%2Forg%2Febd5ce9f178be800ea86b00a82fc04bd.jpg%2F6LZi2Dz10aXZwWVovOT0ULZcn1osQTLGv3YNK792DSs&h=b1138d82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3134527/org/01d52c8d77fb256a04253bbae217a63c.jpg/poCpYN3gmOjo-ix2B95WPeFz_vp5zbX8zfn8tc35_LU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3134527%2Forg%2F01d52c8d77fb256a04253bbae217a63c.jpg%2FpoCpYN3gmOjo-ix2B95WPeFz_vp5zbX8zfn8tc35_LU&h=534b220f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再度復合<br />\n<br />\n其後Paru Paru很快又宣布與女友復合，更揚言要成為一個好男人。不過，他似乎仍沒有動力去認真工作，還發文疑似嘲笑打工仔，令不少網民超火大，有留言更表示「下次女友真的出軌的話，你就別再抱怨了。」<br />\n<br />\n極度懷疑他上輩子是不是拯救了地球... 為甚麼這樣也能有超美的女朋友，還願意再三與他復合。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%90/361428/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8B%B5%E5%BF%97%E5%93%A5-%E6%97%A5%E7%94%B7%E8%82%A5%E7%AA%AE%E9%86%9C%E6%AF%92%E5%8D%BB%E6%93%81%E8%B6%85%E9%9D%9A%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B-%E7%8B%82%E6%99%92%E6%81%A9%E6%84%9B%E7%AB%9F%E6%BF%80%E6%80%92%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91</code></pre>"},{"pid":"f49e7caf8567f18f3cd8bcec5d10cd2231780ee9","tid":1436259,"uid":38737,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D7fP0K5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD7fP0K5.gif&h=58bbf03a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ebebc2a0b6fa40f9b3f5f21c9c34cf5a0d3cbfd","tid":1436259,"uid":135475,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:09:12.000Z","msg":"個肥仔一定有家底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5eeb9f57a707f4f31d7a0f0e21e62298eb457b0","tid":1436259,"uid":31173,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"一般貨色"},{"pid":"2231d2a229d06ad45f9d947b52e3ff9c5da92c2a","tid":1436259,"uid":27670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:09:50.000Z","msg":"睇完個post<br />\n再照下塊鏡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71998e216f93f32911928ad9e14a3e8d2283f9dd","tid":1436259,"uid":90183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:12:16.000Z","msg":"上世唔只救地球 救埋宇宙"},{"pid":"159ea1b5ee6067367be7222b511c9c54808f16ac","tid":1436259,"uid":150610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:12:30.000Z","msg":"一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16cc3a8beae1ee2a364467b70037418b0e6c682","tid":1436259,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji